<figureCitation box="[898,976,898,925]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="21.[151,250,1330,1355]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,174,1310]" captionTargetId="figure@21.[151,1436,174,1310]" captionTargetPageId="21" captionText="FIGURE 12. Family Hydrodromidae, genus Hydrodroma. a.–e. H. lasioderma (MD 154b); a.–b. female and male Cx-I+II; c.–e. integument papillae in various views; f.–i. H. mesembrina (MD 151); f. female Cx-I+II; g.–i. integument papillae in various views; k.–n. H. zhokhovi female; k. Cx-I+II; l.–n. integument papillae in various views." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3613326" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3613326/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
